The paper deals with secure transmission over a multiple antenna Gaussian broadcast channel with confidential messages, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and network security (cs.CR). The use of multiple antennas also involves signal processing (cs.MM) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the characteristics of the channel, which could fall under systems and control (cs.SI).
